snippet.title: Devil May Cry 5 Special Edition - Announcement Trailer | PS5
snippet.description:
DMC is back and better than ever in the series’ most SSStylish and most action-packed entry yet: Devil May Cry 5 Special Edition!

New features include the addition of Dante's brother and arch-rival, Vergil, as a playable character, as well as Turbo Mode, Legendary Dark Knight, Ray Tracing, and more!

https://www.devilmaycry.com/

Rated Mature: Mature - Blood, Partial Nudity, Strong Language, Violence
